'''Been''' ({{lang-en|''lie''}}; {{lang-ar|كذب}}) waa soo gudbinta iyo sheegida [[war]] ama xaalad si khaldan.<ref> name = Merriam-Webster-def Merriam-Webster's Online Dictionary, [http://m-w.com/dictionary/truth truth], 2005</ref> Beenta waxaa ka soo horjeeda [[run]]. Sidoo kale beenta waa sheegida si khaldan (si ka duwan xaqiiqada) dhacdo, war, marxalad iyo wixii la mid ah. Sida caadiga ah, inta ugu badan [[diin|diimaha]], filosofiga, iyo [[cilmi]]gu wuxu aad u dhiirigeliyaan in beenta laga fogaado, iyo in qofku noqdo mid run sheeg ah oo sida xaqiiqada ah wax u sheega.

[[Islaam|Diinta Islaamku]] waxay faraysaa dhamaan dadka muslimiinta ah ineey ahaadaan kuwo runsheeg ah, hadii kale waxay galayaan dembi lagu [[cadaab|ciqaabi]] doono aakhirada.

Guud ahaan, beentu waa soo gudbinta iyo ka waranka dhacdooyinka iyo macluumaadka si khalad ah oo ka duwan xaqiiqada iyo runta.<ref>Oxford English Dictionary (online): Definition of "narrative"</ref>


